A sample project written in Mojolicious (not Lite). 
See koorchik's blog  http://koorchik.blogspot.com/2010/11/mojolicious-lite.html (in Russian)

INSTALLATION
1. Install last version of Mojolicious (from GitHub)
2. Install DBIx::Simple and SQL::Abstract
3. git clone git://github.com/koorchik/FastNotes-Proto.git fastnotes
4. perl fastnotes/script/fastnotes.pl daemon

